Kubernetes!

	Kubernertes is a good solution for container-based architectures as it can solve these issues:
		1. Conttainer availability of essential services
		2. Usage spikes by increasing or decreasing the number of running containers
		3. React to failures of a container
		4. Secure & transparent patching
	
Red Hat OpenShift
	Red Hat OpenShift is a set of modular component and services built on top of Kubernetes
	

